race.description: Country Comfort A Racey Weekend Handicap
race.comment: LORDGIVEMESTRENGTH (11) has been close her past couple, missing over the mile here two back before a 1L defeat at Mt Barker last start. back to 1500m here, but that shouldn't be an issue and she possesses tactical speed to offset the tricky gate. Can get back to winning ways. TIDWELL (4) finished off strongly from midfield to score at Mt Barker last start, breaking his maiden. The draw is a niggle, though the rise in trip should suit and he has plenty of upside. Can build on the last start win. POLYVANOVA (1) brings some strong recent form into this and was beaten in a photo finish at this track and trip three back. Can roll forward from the draw and she's likely to be in this race for a long way. CAPRICIOUS RULER (5) was too good here last start and can build on that effort. KAMIKAZE FIGHTER (6) is better than he showed last time out and can bounce back to his best.
